name: Jira
title: Jira Integration
summary:  >-
  Track, manage, and update Jira tickets directly from New Relic Errors Inbox and CodeStream.
description: >-
  Jira is agile project management software that allows teams of every shape and size to add and change issue types, fields, and workflows. When integrated with the New Relic platform, New Relic One users can easily track, manage, and update their Jira tickets directly from New Relic One with Errors Inbox, or their IDE with CodeStream.
